    <div class="text-2xl font-bold pt-4">Why Ningzy Works?</div>
    <div class="text-l mb-6">As a software engineer, I spend most of my awake hours in front of a computer typing at a
      keyboard. This is why I learned to build a quality keyboard for myself. After doing my homework, I found that
      retail keyboards are overpriced and low-quality, while high end keyboards are just way out of my price range. And
      so, I decided to build my own, and share my passion with the community. I am proud of the effort and care I put
      into the keyboards I build.</div>

